sense.gloss: anatta, anatman, doctrine that states that humans do not possess souls

sdata.j: ↑私↑↓わたし↓は|↑無我|夢中↑↓むがむちゅう↓で↑部屋↑↓へや↓を↑飛↑↓と↓び↑出↑↓だ↓した。
sdata.e: I ran out of the room without knowing what I was doing.

sdata.j: ↑彼↑↓かれ↓はジャズのことになると|↑無我|夢中↑↓むがむちゅう↓になる。
sdata.e: He is so crazy about jazz that he often forgets himself.
